sv:property.sv:value:
This is a newsitem in the products folder, but because of the sitemap mapping for products/**.html it should still be displayed as a detailpage and not as a productpage. This is because the sitemap item contains:

 <sv:property sv:multiple="true"
sv:name="hst:componentconfigurationmappingnames" sv:type="String">
<sv:value>demosite:newsdocument</sv:value>
</sv:property>
<sv:property sv:multiple="true"
sv:name="hst:componentconfigurationmappingvalues" sv:type="String">
<sv:value>hst:pages/detailpage</sv:value>
</sv:property>
